ORDER
Motion for One-day Nunc Pro Tunc Extension of Time to File Petition for Reargument
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 23rd day of June, 2008, the Motion for a One-day, Nunc Pro Tunc Extension of Time to File Petition for Reargument is GRANTED.
Justice TODD did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
